{"tid":637501,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"各位連登仔唔好再笑肥婆手臂一粒粒","createTime":"2018-04-21T22:11:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T03:38:38.000Z","uid":106663,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4edaf789c1d05c0b74c0f509c9df946b1f09df4b","tid":637501,"uid":106663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T22:11:29.000Z","msg":"因為唔係淨係得肥婆先會手臂一粒粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自問算唔上係肥 BMI得17點幾<br />\n但手臂同小腿都好多一粒粒<br />\n呢D一粒粒唔係因為肥婆沖涼沖得唔乾淨 多老泥<br />\n而係因為毛孔角化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為毛囊附近嘅表皮細胞「不正常角化」而導致過量嘅角質蛋白堆積係毛孔上面<br />\n當毛髮被塞係毛孔上嘅角質蛋白&rdquo;kick&rdquo;住生唔到出嚟<br />\n就會產生一粒粒睇落好似整唔走嘅雞皮咁嘅野<br />\n<br />\n其實我身邊識唔少肥人D皮膚都好乾淨好滑<br />\n亦都識個女仔明明瘦到皮包骨咁 但都係成身一粒粒<br />\n所以拜託大家唔好再成日話D肥婆手臂生哂一粒粒咁好肉碌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瘦人都會有咁嘅情況出現<br />\n<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.medpartner.club/keratosis-pilaris-cause-care-treatment/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.medpartner.club%2Fkeratosis-pilaris-cause-care-treatment%2Famp%2F&d=S%2B5kjAccK3kMDDSUh%2FjCFQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=66eb82ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.medpartner.club/keratosis-pilaris-cause-care-treatment/amp/</a>"},{"pid":"497690dbb59d4e0551d076a517f046b381cc5b54","tid":637501,"uid":50253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T22:23:00.000Z","msg":"好想吱返d粒粒出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3763e5f424a061715b2618438fab103905f2f55","tid":637501,"uid":106663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"497690dbb59d4e0551d076a517f046b381cc5b54","tid":637501,"uid":50253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T22:23:00.000Z","msg":"好想吱返d粒粒出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim